<ext_description linkend="Resource_management_arm.Resource_event">
<p>An event that affects the balance or availability of a managed resource. The role
of a resource event is determined by classification.
</p>
<note number="1">
A resource event can be classified as "Planned", "Actual", etc.
</note>
